sql: SELECT oin.order_channel AS orderChannel, oin.payment_dept_code AS deptCode, cd.`name` AS deptName, COUNT(*) AS orderNum, SUM(oin.order_total_pay_price) AS income, (CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(oin.payment_dept_code, 2, 3) = '100' THEN SUBSTRING_INDEX(cd.region_path, ',', -1) WHEN SUBSTRING_INDEX(oin.payment_dept_code, 2, 3) = '210' THEN SUBSTRING_INDEX(cd.region_path, ',', -1) WHEN SUBSTRING_INDEX(oin.payment_dept_code, 2, 3) = '220' THEN SUBSTRING_INDEX(cd.region_path, ',', -1) WHEN SUBSTRING_INDEX(oin.payment_dept_code, 2, 3) = '230' THEN SUBSTRING_INDEX(cd.region_path, ',', -1) ELSE SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(cd.region_path, ',', 2), ',', -1) END) AS areaCode FROM order_info oin LEFT JOIN authentication.csm_dept cd ON payment_dept_code = cd.codenew WHERE '2022-11-24 23:59:59' >= oin.pay_time AND SUBSTRING(oin.payment_dept_code, 2, 3) NOT IN ('852', '285') AND SUBSTRING(oin.payment_dept_code, 1, 1) = '3' GROUP BY subString(payment_dept_code, 2, 6), order_channel ORDER BY oin.payment_dept_code
